OL,3,CMurder probe launched after man, 18,
OL,4,Cfound with stab wound
OL,6,FA murder investigation is underway in
OL,7,FPoole after an 18-year-old man was
OL,8,Ffound with a suspected stab wound.
OL,10,FPolice were called to Longfleet Road
OL,11,Fat 2:13am this morning (Friday 19
OL,12,FJune) where the man was found injured.
OL,14,FHe was taken into hospital for
OL,15,Ftreatment, but died a short time later.
OL,17,FDetectives say it's believed that the
OL,18,Fvictim may have been injured during an
OL,19,Fincident in Dale Close and was then
OL,20,Ftaken to Longfleet Road in a car.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G1/3
