OL,3,CMurder probe launched after man, 18,
OL,4,Cfound with stab wound
OL,6,FA cordon is in place in Dale Close so
OL,7,Fofficers can examine the suspected
OL,8,Fscene.
OL,10,FDetective Superintendent Neil Third,
OL,11,Fof Dorset Police, said: "Our thoughts
OL,12,Fare with the family and friends of the
OL,13,Fyoung man who has tragically died.
OL,15,F"An investigation is underway by
OL,16,Fdetectives and we are working at pace
OL,17,Fto determine the full circumstances of
OL,18,Fwhat has happened.
OL,26,@sD@YOUwD@AOU
