OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F381A1781874674
OL,3,CMurder probe launched after man, 18,
OL,4,Cfound with stab wound
OL,6,F"I would ask anyone who has witnessed
OL,7,Fanything suspicious in Dale Close or
OL,8,FLongfleet Road in the early hours of
OL,9,FFriday 19 June 2026 to please get in
OL,10,Ftouch.
OL,12,F"If any residents or motorists have
OL,13,Fcaptured anything of relevance on
OL,14,Feither home CCTV or dashcam footage,
OL,15,Fplease come forward.
OL,17,F"There will be a heightened police
OL,18,Fpresence in the area while our
OL,19,Fenquiries are carried out and we would
OL,20,Fencourage anyone with information or
OL,21,Fconcerns to please speak with us."
